timelineData.query: SELECT `buyers`.`id`, `buyer_name`, `buyer_details`.`cc` as `cc`, SUM(buyer_details.buyer_qty) as total_qty, SUM(buy_cost) as buy_cost, SUM(buy_cost * buyer_details.buyer_qty) as total_buy_cost FROM `buyer_details` JOIN `buyers` ON `buyers`.`id` = `buyer_details`.`buyer` JOIN `purchase_items` ON `purchase_items`.`id` = `buyer_details`.`purchase_id` JOIN `lead_lists` ON `lead_lists`.`id` = `purchase_items`.`lead_id` WHERE `purchase_items`.`created_at` >= '2024-02-01 00:00:00' AND `purchase_items`.`created_at` <= '2024-02-21 23:59:59' AND `lead_lists`.`file_id` = '33' GROUP BY `buyer_details`.`cc`

timelineData.query: SELECT YEAR(purchase_items.created_at) as year, MONTHNAME(purchase_items.created_at) as month, SUM(purchase_items.qty) as qty, SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.buy_cost) as buy_cost, SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.market_price) as sell_price, SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.profit) as profit, ((SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.profit) / SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.market_price))*0.6) * 100 as margin, ((SUM(purchase_items.qty* lead_lists.profit) / SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.buy_cost))*100) as roi FROM `purchase_items` JOIN `lead_lists` ON `lead_lists`.`id` = `purchase_items`.`lead_id` WHERE YEAR(purchase_items.created_at) = YEAR(NOW()) AND `lead_lists`.`file_id` = '33' GROUP BY YEAR(purchase_items.created_at), MONTH(purchase_items.created_at)
